                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1720-18420509 t18420509-1720-punishment-272"></join>Confined Three Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
